    "en": "Sevoflurane is a clear, colorless, and mobile liquid. It is miscible with ethanol (99.5). It is very slightly soluble in water. It is volatile and not inflammable. D Refractive index n20: 1.2745 – 1.2760 Boiling point: about 58.69C"
